{},"article":{},"index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"《刘少奇言论》后来以“人民出版社资料室”名义出版，《出版说明》中没有点邓小平的名字。"}],"contents":[{"id":"6460cf5c5b","type":"title","text":"对陈伯达、江青关于选编《刘少奇言论》报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"3b3431022d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"57802f96eb","type":"paragraph","text":"林彪、恩来P同志阅后，退陈伯达同志办理。《说明》中，不提邓小平。是否妥当，请的定。以什么机关为出版单位的问题，请在一次会议上商定。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"3b3431022d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2a351da755","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"3b3431022d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6ed31be52f","type":"paragraph","text":"十月九日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"3b3431022d","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":119,"end":119}},"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"48309825c2","type":"paragraph","text":"林彪、恩来同志阅后，退陈伯达同志办理。《说明》中，不提邓小平。是否妥当，请酌定。以什么机关为出版单位的问题，请在一次会议上商定。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3b3431022d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"aed8170bec","type":"title","text":"对陈伯达、江青关于选编《刘少奇言论》报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3b3431022d","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}